<paragraph id="1124DA89A2DBB51775C12927F592CF99" pageNumber="10">Etymology: The specific epithet is a patronym honoring Marcelo T. Tavares, professor and researcher of Chalcididae at Universidade Federal do Espirito Santo, Brazil.</paragraph>
